  "name": "Rolotia",
  "title": "Timeless Beauty",
  "secondName": "Timeless Beauty",
  "description": "Many people start the new year with self-reflection. With resolute hearts, they set out to be new people, free of the vices that have held them back. Rolotia observes these resolutions with glee, even knowing most of them will be broken. The first days of a year have a purity to them, a power that makes any dream appear within reach. If a single person sees their promises through, none of their failed resolutions were wasted.\n\nShe's no stranger to wanting a second chance.",
